{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas fazzija us winnu:\nDabbu man weenu treju Gaddu\nGohțixu/ un weenu Kasu no trim\nGaddeem/ un weenu Aunu no\ntrim Gaddeem/ un weenu Uhbeli/\nun weenu jaunu Ballodi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch dabbuja tam\ncho wisfu/ un wiꞥſch dallija tohs\nwiddu puſcham/ un likke ikkatru\nDaſtu ween prettohtru/ bet tohs\nPutnus ne dallija wiꞥſch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee Maitas Putni no-\naiđahs us tahm/ un Ahbrams no-\nsinne tohs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad ta Saute nogah-\n/ tad kritte zeets Meegs us Ah-\nramu/ un reds Istruhzinaſcha-\na/ un leela Tumfiba kritte pahr\ninnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us Ah-\nramu: Scho finui teefcham/ ka\nws Dsimmuus fivesch buhs\nhdâ Semmê/ kas tam ne pee-\nrr/ un tee kalpohs winneem/ un\ninzi teem gruhti darrihs tschetre-\nnts Gaddus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr es arridsan fołdi-\nhz to Tantu/ kam tee kalpohs/ un\nhz to isees tee ar leelu Mantu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu eei pee taweem Teh-\neem ar Meeru/ (un) tapti ap-\nkts labbâ Wezzuma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas zettorta Muhscha\nugums nahks atkał schai Wee-\njo ta Ahmoriteru Netaifniba\nlihds fchim wehl ne peepildita.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikke / kad ta\naule nogahje un Tumfiba met-\nhs/ tad redsi/ tur bija weens\nhmains Zeplis/ un weena Ug-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "guns Leesma/ kas zaue ſcheem\nDalteem zaue gahje.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tanni Deena darrija tas\nKUNGS Derribu ar Ahbramu/\nfazzidans: Tawam Dsimmu-\nman efmu escho Semmi dewis/\nno tahs Egiptes Uppes/ lihds tai\nleelai Uppet Wrat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Keniterus/un tohs Ke-\nnisiterus/ un tohs Kadmoniterus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tohs Eetiterus/ un tohs\nWeresiterus/ un tohs Rewaim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tohs Ahmoriterus/ un\ntohs Kananiterus/ un tohs Gir-\ngositerus/ un tohs Jebusiterus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XVI. Nodalla.\nSara dohd Ahbramam fawu Kalponi Ahgari\npar Seewu: 1. Ta tohp gruhta: 4. Un\nbehg nohst no fawas Gaspaschas: 7. Bet us\nta Engeta Pawehleschanu ta atgreeschahs at-\npakat: 8. Tas apfohla winnai fawa Dsim-\nmuma Wairoshana: 10. Dsemde Ismäelu: 15.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Sarai Ahbrama See-\nwa ne dsemdeja tant ne\nneeka/ un tai bija weena\nEgipteru Kalpone Ahgare Wahrdâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sarai fazzija uhs Ah-\nbramu: Rangi jelle/tas KUNGS\nirr mann atsflehdsis/ ka es ne\ndsemdeju/ eij jelle pee mannas\nKalpones/ jaſchu es zaue winnas\napbehrnota tapschu/un Ahbrams\nklansija Sarajas Balsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nehme Sarai Ahbrama\nSeeva to Ahgari fawu Egipteru\nKalponi/ pehz Defimits Gaddeem/\nkad Ahbrams eeksch tahs Semmes\nKanaan bij Dsihwojts/ un dewe to\nAhbramam fawani Wihran par\nSeewu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch gabje pee Ahga-\nres/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
